videos.headline: Ole Miss QB tosses 58-yard TD on opening drive
videos.description: Jordan Ta'amu completes a pass to D.K. Metcalf for a 58-yard Ole Miss touchdown.

videos.headline: Ole Miss' Jaylon Jones returns kickoff 94 yards for TD
videos.description: Jaylon Jones fields the kickoff and returns it 94-yards for an Ole Miss touchdown.

videos.headline: Texas Tech's QB goes down after collision
videos.description: Texas Tech quarterback McLane Carter exits the game after taking hard hit in the first quarter against Ole Miss.

videos.headline: Ole Miss's RB gallops in for a 65-yard TD run
videos.description: Ole Miss running back Scottie Phillips avoids Texas Tech defender for a 65-yards TD run.

videos.headline: Ole Miss QB Ta'amu  completes 34-yard TD pass

videos.headline: Vasher's OBJ-like grab impresses booth
videos.description: Mark Jones and Dusty Dvoracek are as stunned as anyone by Texas Tech wideout T.J. Vasher's highlight-reel catch.
